org.webcurator.ui.admin.command
Class RoleCommand

java.lang.Object
  org.webcurator.ui.admin.command.RoleCommand

public class RoleCommand
extends java.lang.Object

holds the Role base information gathered from the UI related to User Roles within the WCT system. A Role is comprised of a set of Privileges to different functions within the system.

Author:
bprice
